    "description": "藉由實作讓同學了解化工裝置理論與實務之相互配合與印證，從中熟悉化工裝置之基本操作、維護與管理，培養實驗廢棄物減量及污染防治之概念與習慣，使同學具備對工作職業安全、衛生知識及環保的理解與實踐。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.\t工廠安全防護演練<br>2.\t配管操作<br>3.\t流體輸送裝置操作─離心泵<br>4.\t流體輸送裝置操作─壓縮機<br>5.\t流量測量─流量計組合實驗<br>6.\t流體流動操作─雷諾數實驗裝置<br>7.\t流體流動操作─流體流動實驗裝置操作<br>8.\t熱交換器操作─雙套管熱交換器<br>9.\t熱交換器操作─殼館熱交換器<br>10.\t真空蒸發裝置操作<br>11.\t蒸餾裝置操作<br>",
        "en": "1.\tFactory Safety Protection Drill<br>2.\tPiping Operation<br>3.\tFluid Transport Device Operation – Centrifugal Pump<br>4.\tFluid Transport Device Operation – Compressor<br>5.\tFlow Measurement – Flowmeter Combination Experiment<br>6.\tFluid Flow Operation – Reynolds Number Experimental Device<br>7.\tFluid Flow Operation – Fluid Flow Experimental Device Operation<br>8.\tHeat Exchanger Operation – Double Pipe Heat Exchanger<br>9.\tHeat Exchanger Operation – Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger<br>10.\tVacuum Evaporation Device Operation<br>11.\tDistillation Device Operation<br>"
    },
